name: Unidentified_Wookiee_bartender
content:
A Wookiee bartender worked at a cantina located in the capital city of the Inner Rim planet Pijal during the Republic Era. By 40 BBY, the Wookiee worked alongside Selbie, one of the establishment's hostesses. The Jedi Lord Regent Rael Averross described the cantina that the bartender worked at as a muddy hole carved out of a dingy rock that smelled like the Wookiee.
The Wookiee bartender was mentioned in Master & Apprentice, a 2019 novel written by Claudia Gray.
